
{center}
{subhead} AAA Awards Voting - Now With A Grand Prize Raffle!{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

For Immediate Release{p}
Permission Granted To Redistribute Without Alteration
{p} {p}
Contact:{p}
Martin Sahlén - director@aaa-awards.org, +46-8-673 73 23{p}
Director, The AAA Awards
{p} {p}
Stockholm, Sweden - Thursday, May 20, 1999.{p}
It's time to cast your vote for the AAA Awards 1998! Do it now, and you
could be the lucky winner of a brand new, specially designed and
hand-airbrushed Amiga 1200HDD, or one of twenty copies of Cloanto's
"Amiga Forever Online Edition"! The AAA Awards 1998 are proudly
presented in association with AMIGA and Cloanto.
{p} {p}
Voting
{p} {p}
Voting is open for everyone until June 30, around the clock. These
options are available:
{p} {p}
- Online: {link http://www.aaa-awards.org}http://www.aaa-awards.org{end}{p}
- Phone: +46-90-71 00 20 (24 hours){p}
- Fax: +46-90-71 01 46{p}
- Mail: Amiga Format #125 July 1999 and other magazines will contain
mail-in forms
{p} {p}
This year's categories are{p}
	AAA Award International{p}
	AAA Award Belgium{p}
	AAA Award Spain{p}
	AAA Award Sweden{p}
	AAA Award United Kingdom
{p} {p}
Prize Raffle
{p} {p}
Once you vote for the AAA Award International 1998, we'll automatically
place you in the raffle to win...
{p} {p}
* A brand new, specially designed, hand-airbrushed Amiga 1200 HDD{p}
* One of twenty copies of Cloanto's "Amiga Forever Online Edition"
{p} {p}
You could be the lucky winner!
{p} {p}
Award ceremonies
{p} {p}
The AAA Awards 1998 Winners will be presented at these locations:{p}
AAA Award International, July 24-25{p}
	World of Amiga 99, The Kensington Town Hall Conference Centre, London, UK{p}
AAA Award Belgium, July 8{p}
	Waaslandia Merksem meeting, Café Pierre De Deken, Merksem, Belgium{p}
AAA Award Spain, October 29-November 1{p}
	Radykal Amiga Party, Armilla (Granada), Spain{p}
AAA Award Sweden, August 7-15{p}
	Stora Nolia fair, Umeå, Sweden{p}
AAA Award United Kingdom, July 24-25{p}
	World of Amiga 99, The Kensington Town Hall Conference Centre, London, UK{p}
{p} {p}
See our homepage {link http://www.aaa-awards.org}http://www.aaa-awards.org{end} for exact dates and times.
{p} {p}
Juries
{p} {p}
The AAA Awards Committee would like to take this opportunity to thank
all jury members throughout the world for their effort.
